" data-lazy-srcset=\"/media/2025/02/BMW-iX-Design-Sketch-Render-03-720x384.jpg 720w, /media/2025/02/BMW-iX-Design-Sketch-Render-03-234x125.jpg 234w, /media/2025/02/BMW-iX-Design-Sketch-Render-03-355x190.jpg 355w, /media/2025/02/BMW-iX-Design-Sketch-Render-03-768x410.jpg 768w, /media/2025/02/BMW-iX-Design-Sketch-Render-03-1536x820.jpg 1536w, /media/2025/02/BMW-iX-Design-Sketch-Render-03.jpg 1920w\" data-lazy-src=\"/media/2025/02/BMW-iX-Design-Sketch-Render-03-720x384.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe M70 xDrive variant introduces blacked-out elements, an illuminated BMW Iconic Glow grille, and exclusive 22-inch alloy wheels, reinforcing its performance-driven character.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eA new range of metallic finishes, including Arctic Race Blue, Carbon Black, and Frozen Deep Grey, complements the BMW iXâ€™s sculptural form, reinforcing its cutting-edge, all-electric identity.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong data-start=\"4\" data-end=\"58\"\u003eInterior Design\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.carbodydesign.com/gallery/2025/02/the-new-bmw-ix/18/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.carbodydesign.com/media/2025/02/BMW-iX-xDrive60-Interior-05-720x540.jpg\" width=\"720\" height=\"540\" alt=\"BMW iX xDrive60 Interior\" srcset=\"https://www.carbodydesign.com/media/2025/02/BMW-iX-xDrive60-Interior-05-720x540.jpg 720w, https://www.carbodydesign.com/media/2025/02/BMW-iX-xDrive60-Interior-05-234x176.jpg 234w, https://www.carbodydesign.com/media/2025/02/BMW-iX-xDrive60-Interior-05-355x266.jpg 355w, https://www.carbodydesign.com/media/2025/02/BMW-iX-xDrive60-Interior-05-120x90.jpg 120w, https://www.carbodydesign.com/media/2025/02/BMW-iX-xDrive60-Interior-05-768x576.jpg 768w, https://www.carbodydesign.com/media/2025/02/BMW-iX-xDrive60-Interior-05-1536x1153.jpg 1536w, https://www.carbodydesign.com/media/2025/02/BMW-iX-xDrive60-Interior-05.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"auto, (min-width: 1900px) 90vw, (max-width: 760px) 100vw, 720px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%20720%20540\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"/media/2025/02/BMW-iX-xDrive60-Interior-05-720x540.jpg 720w, /media/2025/02/BMW-iX-xDrive60-Interior-05-234x176.jpg 234w, /media/2025/02/BMW-iX-xDrive60-Interior-05-355x266.jpg 355w, /media/2025/02/BMW-iX-xDrive60-Interior-05-120x90.jpg 120w, /media/2025/02/BMW-iX-xDrive60-Interior-05-768x576.jpg 768w, /media/2025/02/BMW-iX-xDrive60-Interior-05-1536x1153.jpg 1536w, /media/2025/02/BMW-iX-xDrive60-Interior-05.jpg 1920w\" data-lazy-src=\"/media/2025/02/BMW-iX-xDrive60-Interior-05-720x540.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe BMW iX interior blends spaciousness, minimalist aesthetics, and advanced technology. The cabin features frameless glass surfaces, floating center console, and a curved BMW Live Cockpit display, creating a modern, open atmosphere.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.carbodydesign.com/gallery/2025/02/the-new-bmw-ix/16/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.carbodydesign.com/media/2025/02/BMW-iX-xDrive60-Interior-03-720x540.jpg\" width=\"720\" height=\"540\" alt=\"BMW iX xDrive60 Interior\" srcset=\"https://www.carbodydesign.com/media/2025/02/BMW-iX-xDrive60-Interior-03-720x540.jpg 720w, https://www.carbodydesign.com/media/2025/02/BMW-iX-xDrive60-Interior-03-234x176.jpg 234w, https://www.carbodydesign.com/media/2025/02/BMW-iX-xDrive60-Interior-03-355x266.jpg 355w, https://www.carbodydesign.com/media/2025/02/BMW-iX-xDrive60-Interior-03-120x90.jpg 120w, https://www.carbodydesign.com/media/2025/02/BMW-iX-xDrive60-Interior-03-768x576.jpg 768w, https://www.carbodydesign.com/media/2025/02/BMW-iX-xDrive60-Interior-03-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://www.carbodydesign.com/media/2025/02/BMW-iX-xDrive60-Interior-03.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"auto, (min-width: 1900px) 90vw, (max-width: 760px) 100vw, 720px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%20720%20540\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"/media/2025/02/BMW-iX-xDrive60-Interior-03-720x540.jpg 720w, /media/2025/02/BMW-iX-xDrive60-Interior-03-234x176.jpg 234w, /media/2025/02/BMW-iX-xDrive60-Interior-03-355x266.jpg 355w, /media/2025/02/BMW-iX-xDrive60-Interior-03-120x90.jpg 120w, /media/2025/02/BMW-iX-xDrive60-Interior-03-768x576.jpg 768w, /media/2025/02/BMW-iX-xDrive60-Interior-03-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, /media/2025/02/BMW-iX-xDrive60-Interior-03.jpg 1600w\" data-lazy-src=\"/media/2025/02/BMW-iX-xDrive60-Interior-03-720x540.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eM Sport seats with microfibre/Sensatec upholstery, an M leather steering wheel, and Dark Silver trim accents enhance the sporty appeal. Premium options include a Sky Lounge panoramic glass roof, Bowers \u0026amp; Wilkins Diamond Surround Sound System, and ambient lighting.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eKey features include:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eBMW Operating System 8.5 with iDrive for intuitive touch and voice control.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e5G connectivity, BMW Digital Key, and My BMW App integration.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAdvanced driver assistance systems, including Level 2+ Highway Assistant and Automated Parking Assistant.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003ePerformance and Efficiency\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe dual-motor all-wheel drive system has been refined for increased power across all models:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003exDrive45: 408 hp (300 kW), 0-100 km/h in 5.1 sec\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003exDrive60: 544 hp (400 kW), 0-100 km/h in 4.6 sec\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eM70 xDrive: 659 hp (485 kW), 0-100 km/h in 3.8 sec\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe battery technology has been improved, with the xDrive45 now offering a 30% increase in capacity (94.8 kWh), while higher trims feature 109 kWh packs. Efficiency enhancements include new power electronics, lower rolling resistance tires, and adaptive recuperation.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCharging speeds have increased, with DC fast charging up to 195 kW, enabling significant range recovery in minutes. The BMW iX also supports intelligent navigation, optimizing routes based on available charging stations.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e(Source: BMW)\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
